{"tid":1886933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(武漢肺炎) 中共連累所有「亞洲人」在美國被歧視","createTime":"2020-02-19T08:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T20:25:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":100,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"d562565534b7f5683847810324bd440b327281e7","tid":1886933,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:39:08.000Z","msg":"中共犯錯爆出武漢肺炎, 連累所有「亞洲人」在美國被歧視  , 整個亞裔族群也被染上污名<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200219/IHCNROIYOWG7DRLHHNPW3VF5Y4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200219%2FIHCNROIYOWG7DRLHHNPW3VF5Y4%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=1dce2ea7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200219%2FIHCNROIYOWG7DRLHHNPW3VF5Y4%2F&h=36ea7a29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200219/IHCNROIYOWG7DRLHHNPW3VF5Y4/</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】病毒撕破平等假象 加州學童被打到入院<br />\n9小時前<br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）美國號稱民族熔爐，加州更是箇中翹楚，以開明包容的多元文化見稱，但一切或許只是假象。武漢肺炎爆發後，美國錄得15宗確診病例，8宗位於加州；當地近月發生多宗種族歧視事件，有亞裔學生遭到欺凌，被打到入院，成為最大受害者。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林宜萱<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯KCAL-TV前新聞主播、<strong>來自越南的阮雷娜</strong>（Leyna Nguyen，音譯）表示，兒子穆里亞諾（Dylan Muriano）就讀洛杉磯聯合學區的沃特里德中學（Walter Reed Middle School）八年級，周三在學校飲水不小心嗆到，因此咳嗽，被老師要求去醫療室，但其他咳嗽的學生，都沒有被如此要求。<br />\n<br />\n在醫療室內，穆里亞諾向醫生澄清自己沒有肺炎，只是飲水嗆到；醫生也相當不耐煩，翻了個白眼並告訴他，「每個人都很超級敏感」。<br />\n<br />\n穆里亞諾回到教室後，被同學嘲笑身上帶有新型冠狀病毒，老師也很不高興看見他回到課室，繼續無視他。最後，穆里亞諾問老師，是否因為他是亞洲人，所以把他送到醫療室，但老師不予理會。隔日，這位老師以「干擾他人（disruptivez）」的理由將穆里亞諾送到校長辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n阮雷娜表示，穆里亞諾平時臉皮很厚，不是「玻璃心」孩子，事件不是因為兒子過度敏感而起，而是一個不夠敏感的老師造成。阮雷娜在facebook公開這事，並發現亞裔遭歧視事件暴增，例如在雜貨店內、在飛機上，幾乎沒人想有亞洲人在身邊。<br />\n<br />\n同樣在洛杉磯，一名有亞洲背景的16歲學生，被質疑身上有新型冠狀病毒，在學校遭到毆打，送到急症室接受磁力共振（MRI）檢查，當局暫未公布他的傷勢、所屬學校及其他細節。洛杉磯聯合學區和相關官員，已開始調查穆里亞諾的遭遇和這宗攻擊事件。<br />\n<br />\n另外，路透報道在洛杉磯縣卡森市（Carson），有人製作假傳單，呼籲大家避免到中式連鎖餐館熊貓快餐（Panda Express）這類有亞洲元素的商店消費，上面還蓋有偽造的世衞印章。當地不少民眾深信不疑，有醫生表示，病人詢問是否應該要避免到熊貓快餐用餐；Twitter上也不少這類「笑話」，例如「我要一份不加冠狀病毒的熊貓快餐」。<br />\n<br />\n華裔人口眾多的阿罕布拉市（Alhambra），至今沒有傳出過疫情，卻有超過1.4萬人聯署，要求關閉該學區學校。實際上，加州雖有8宗確診武漢肺炎病例，但僅其中一宗位於洛杉磯地區，病人已經隔離治療，而洛杉磯人口多達1,010萬。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>目前，網上充斥「華人很噁心（chinese people are so disgusting）」、「只有華人身上有新型冠狀病毒（only chinese people have the coronavirus）」等言論。整個亞裔族群也被染上污名，畢竟對不少西方人而言，亞洲人面孔不易區分，更別提口音或文化差異，「Chinese」一詞幾乎就代表所有會說中文或過農曆新年的亞洲人。</strong><br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯縣人際關係委員會執行主任托馬（Robin Toma）強調，人們對於偏見，必須自覺地進行自我反省，做任何事情之前，先思考動機是否來自刻板印象或恐懼。然而最大問題是，人們如何才懂得「自覺」。"},{"pid":"123ff3a544e7b671bd95409b1221f8dc54a5bd03","tid":1886933,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7b3cd00e01c4461ea4063b0ef95b6d14c0086a","tid":1886933,"uid":167548,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:40:05.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Is Not China"},{"pid":"82462a5d0a41e0ad45f52f30b47d0cd63339db7b","tid":1886933,"uid":76705,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"Leftard: Only black lives matter<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785c071aa8fbd98e3c57ce7aa014559314722ba0","tid":1886933,"uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"fd7b3cd00e01c4461ea4063b0ef95b6d14c0086a","tid":1886933,"uid":167548,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:40:05.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Is Not China"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:43:55.000Z","msg":"好多西方人唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n越南人都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbsnews.com/news/coronavirus-bullies-attack-asian-teen-los-angeles-accusing-him-of-having-coronavirus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fcoronavirus-bullies-attack-asian-teen-los-angeles-accusing-him-of-having-coronavirus%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=717ed01c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbsnews.com/news/coronavirus-bullies-attack-asian-teen-los-angeles-accusing-him-of-having-coronavirus/</a><br />\n<br />\nIn a similar incident, a Vietnamese-American eighth grader in Los Angeles named Dylan Muriano was sent to the nurse's office at his middle school on Wednesday because he coughed from swallowing water.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;He actually said to me, 'all the other students who are coughing, they don't get sent out.' But they're not Asian,&quot; the boy's mother, longtime L.A. news anchor Leyna Nguyen, told Fox 11.<br />\n<br />\nTo make matters worse, when the nurse cleared Muriano to return to his classroom, the eighth grader alleges that his peers teased him about having coronavirus."},{"pid":"1e235b2bbd5cb60211d97ace1d1095181cb33fa5","tid":1886933,"uid":265179,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1zAuCV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1zAuCV.gif&h=500f5237&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbcc9662a977348bcb375830d9f3f7dd05992933","tid":1886933,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:44:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">求入去幫推及rt + like + reply</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【19/2 twitter *極度*要人】美國議員全方位怒插中共<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1886899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1886899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f92e58b3bafed6959dabbe435a0d2f27890049f","tid":1886933,"uid":997,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"fd7b3cd00e01c4461ea4063b0ef95b6d14c00